 your bank, Sepa EUR transfers can take a few minutes to be approved. Longer delays can be expected at weekends. <\/p>\n    <p>Once we receive the funds, your wallet account will be automatically credited and you will receive a confirmation via email.<\/p>","transaction_in_progress_message_upi_direct":"<p>We are now processing your UPI transaction. This can take up to 30 mins for confirmation. <\/p>\n                                                  <p>We will notify you via email once the process is completed.<\/p>","transaction_failed_message":"The transaction is failed. Please contact support if you need further information.","use_a_stored_card":"Use a stored card","please_select_your_stored_card":"Please select your card from the dropdown menu.","select_stored_card":"Select Stored Card or Use New Card:","select":"Select","select_a_stored_card_from_the_dropdown":"Select a stored card from the dropdown above or use a new card from the fields below.","enter_card_detail":"Enter Card Details","please_enter_your_details":"Please enter your details in the required boxes as shown and then press the <strong>Confirm<\/strong> button.","please_enter_your_details_2":"Please enter your details in the required boxes as shown and then press the <strong>Pay<\/strong> button.","card_number":"Card Number:","expiry_date":"Expiry Date:","month":"Month","year":"Year","card_detail":"Card Detail:","card_holder_name":"Cardholder Name:","as_shown_on_card":"(As shown on card)","cvv_number":"CVV Number:","last_3_digits":"(Last 3 digits on rear of card)","save_card_details":"Save Card Details:","save_upi_info":"Save UPI Account Details:","select_upi_id":"UPI Account List","add_new_upi_account":"Add New Upi Account","would_you_like_to_save_this_card":"Would you like to save this card for future payments?","please_tick_to_confirm":"Please tick to confirm.","netteller_account_detail":"Neteller Account Details","bank_account_detail":"To ensure we match this deposit with your WeLoveLotto accoun