act amount of <span class=\"transfer-amount\"><\/span> to the following bank account","note_desc2":"Ensure your Description Code is entered in transfer description content.","note_desc3":"Please click <b>Confirm<\/b> button once your transaction has been completed.","note_desc4":"Please ensure your reference code <span class=\"transfer-code\"><\/span><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Copy\" style=\"margin-left: 5px\"><i class=\"fa fa-copy\"><\/i><\/a> is entered in the Note of the transaction","note_desc5":"Ensure your network is correct otherwise you can lose your asset.","note_desc6":"Once the transaction is completed. Please enter your Transaction ID (TxID) and click \"<b>Confirm<\/b>\" button","note_desc_upi1_desktop":"Please use your UPI application and scan the below QR. Make sure you transfer the exact amount of <span class=\"transfer-amount\"><\/span> to our UPI account and click on <b>\"Next Step\"<\/b> button","note_desc_upi1_mobile":"Please use your UPI application to scan the QR code below or tap the \u201cPay via UPI apps\u201d button to pay directly through a UPI application. Make sure you transfer the exact amount of <span class=\"transfer-amount\"><\/span> to our UPI account, then tap the <b>\u201cNext Step\u201d<\/b> button to proceed to the next stage.","note_desc_upi_expire_time":"The QR code will be expired in <span class=\"qr-expire-time\"><\/span>","note_desc_upi_is_expired":"The QR code is expired","note_desc_upi2":"Please click <b>Next Step<\/b> button once your transaction has been completed.","note_desc_upi3":"Enter the 12-digit UTR (UPI Transaction ID or Reference No. depends on your UPI app) and click on <b>Confirm<\/b> button.","note_desc_upi4":"<b>IMPORTANT:<\/b> Your deposit transaction won't be success until you supply the UTR and click on \"Confirm\" button","guilding_text_upi_desktop":"1. Please use your UPI app to scan the QR code below to complete the payment.<br>\n                                2. Once the payment is done, 