ered your card)","postcode_note":"*Recommend to input correct postcode to increase success rate","please_select_verify_option":"Please select verification option.","deposit_description_select_verify_option":"Please choose one of the card verification options: ","enter_upi_account_detail":"Enter UPI Account Detail","note_upi":"**Please enter your UPI account information correctly to improve the success rate of your deposits.","upi_id":"UPI ID (Required)","upi_id_max":"UPI ID may not be greater than 255 characters","upi_id_invalid":"Please input valid UPI ID","upi_account_username":"UPI Account Name (Required)","upi_account_fullname":"UPI Account Full Name (Required)","upi_account_email":"UPI Account Email (Required)","upi_account_phone":"UPI Account Phone (Required)","upi_account_full_name_is_required":"Account full name is required","upi_account_user_name_is_required":"Account name is required","upi_id_is_required":"UPI ID is required","upi_account_email_is_required":"Email address is required","upi_account_phone_is_required":"Phone number is required","upi_account_full_name_max":"Account full name may not be greater than 100 characters.","upi_account_user_name_max":"Account user name may not be greater than 100 characters.","upi_account_email_max":"Email address may not be greater than 100 characters.","upi_account_phone_max":"Phone number may not be greater than 16 characters.","upi_account_email_invalid":"Please input valid email","upi_account_phone_invalid":"Please input valid mobile number","gateway_suspended_error":"This payment gateway is temporarily unavailable. We will inform you via email when it becomes available.","upi_id_placeholder":"Enter Your UPI ID","upi_account_username_placeholder":"Enter Your Name","upi_account_email_placeholder":"Enter email address associated with your upi account","upi_account_phone_placeholder":"Enter number without first 0 digit","click_to_choose_upi_id":"Click to choose upi account","vouchstar_amount_too_low":"Your deposit 